@page "/mrqueen"

<div class="containerHold">
	<img style = "width: 100%; height: 95%;"src="assets/mrqueen/hero.png">
	<div class="heroText">
		<h1>Mr. Queen</h1>
		<div>
			<p>Directed by Yoon Sung-sik, it stars Shin Hye-sun as Queen Cheorin 
				and Kim Jung-hyun as King Cheoljong. The drama is about Queen 
				Cheorin finding herself with the soul of a modern-day man inside
				her body, and King Cheoljong striving to be a king who helps his
				people.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<body>
	<div class="layout">
		<button style="display: inline-block">
			<img src="assets/AddToCollection.png" />
		</button>
		<button style="display: inline-block">
			<img src="assets/MonkeChat.png" />
		</button>
		<div class="medDivider"></div>
		<Row>
			<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.Is8">
				<Row>
					<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.IsQuarter">
						<h4>GENRE</h4>
						<p>Romantic, Period Piece</p>
					</Column>
					<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.IsQuarter">
						<h4>LANGUAGE</h4>
						<p>Korean</p>
					</Column>
					<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.IsQuarter">
						<h4>LOCATION</h4>
						<p>South Korea</p>
					</Column>
					<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.IsQuarter">
						<h4>PLATFORM</h4>
						<p>Netflix</p>
					</Column>
				</Row>
			</Column>
		</Row>
		<div class="bigDivider"></div>
		<!--Begin Highlights-->
		<h2>Highlights</h2>
		<div class="bigYellowDivider"></div>
		<div class="blankDivider"></div>
		<Row>
			<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.IsQuarter">
				<Link To="#1">
					<img src="assets/mrqueen/Highlight1.png" />
				</Link>
			</Column>
			<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.IsQuarter">
				<img src="assets/mrqueen/Highlight2.png" />
			</Column>
			<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.IsQuarter">
				<img src="assets/mrqueen/Highlight3.png" />
			</Column>
			<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.IsQuarter">
				<img src="assets/mrqueen/Highlight4.png" />
			</Column>
		</Row>
		<div id="1" class="medDivider"></div>
		<!--Start enlarged-->
		<h3>Gungnamji Pond</h3>
		<div class="yellowDivider"></div>
		<div class="medDivider"></div>
		<Row>
			<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.Is5">
				<img src="assets/mrqueen/Highlight1_Enlarged.png" />
			</Column>
			<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.Is7">
				<Row>
					<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.Is1">
						<img style="padding-left: 23px;"src="assets/Location.png" />
					</Column>
					<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.Is11">
						<h2>Gungnamji Pond<img style="float: right" src="assets/Link.png"></h2>
						<h2>궁남지</h2>
						<div class="blankDivider"></div>
						<p>
							A key turning point in Mr. Queen when Bong-hwan (Choi Jin-hyuk) fell into the pool.
							It later transported him to the Joseon Dynasty.
							<br /><br />
							Historically, the story centers around Chundangji Lake in Seoul, however filming
							took place in Buyeo.
						</p>
					</Column>
				</Row>

			</Column>
		</Row>

		<div class="bigDivider"></div>
		<!--Start chat-->
		<h2>Monkey Business</h2>
		<div class="bigYellowDivider"></div>
		<div class="medDivider"></div>
		<Row>
			<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.Is3">
				<div class="visits" style="padding-left: 30px;">
					<h3>Visits</h3>
					<div class="blankDivider"></div>
					<button onclick="@seen">
						<img src="assets/MonkeSee.png" />
					</button>
					<div class="blankDivider"></div>
					<button onclick="@did">
						<img src="assets/MonkeDid.png" />
					</button>

					<div class="medDivider"></div>
					<h3><img src="assets/Eye.png" /><b>	@seeValue%	</b>Monke See</h3>
					<h3><img src="assets/Eye_Off.png" /><b>	@didValue%	</b>Monke Did</h3>
				</div>
			</Column>
			<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.Is8">
				<h3>Chat</h3>
				<div class="blankDivider"></div>
				<TextEdit Placeholder="Ex. This location was bananas!"></TextEdit>
				<div class="bigDivider"></div>
				<div class="medDivider"></div>
				<div style="padding-left:200px;">
					<Row>
						<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.Is2">
							<img src="assets/SampleProfile1.png" />
						</Column>
						<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.Is10">
							<h2>@at()JennyChen32</h2>
							<div class="blankDivider"></div>
							<h5>Los Angeles, CA, USA</h5>
							<div class="blankDivider"></div>
							<p>
								Mr. Queen has long been one of my favorite K-Dramas. When I had the 
								opportunity to travel to South Korea, I decided to visit some iconic 
								landmarks that I once dreamed of. The ease and access of finding these 
								locations through Movie Monkey allowed for less stress. Woohoo! Great trip ~~
							</p>
						</Column>
					</Row>
					<div class="medDivider"></div>
					<Row>
						<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.Is2">
							<img src="assets/SampleProfile2.png" />
						</Column>
						<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.Is10">
							<h2>@at()happigeon</h2>
							<div class="blankDivider"></div>
							<h5>Seattle, WA, USA</h5>
							<div class="blankDivider"></div>
							<p>
								Byeongsan Seowon was definitely the highlight of my Korea trip. 
								Glad to see it on Movie Monkey.
							</p>
						</Column>
					</Row>
					<div class="medDivider"></div>
					<Row>
						<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.Is2">
							<img src="assets/SampleProfile3.png" />
						</Column>
						<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.Is10">
							<h2>@at()StannisTheMannis32</h2>
							<div class="blankDivider"></div>
							<h5>Hong Kong, Hong Kong</h5>
							<div class="blankDivider"></div>
							<p>
								Being able to visit locations you once saw on screen is a privilege 
								like no other, and I’m glad Movie Monkey opened these doors. Hoping 
								to add more locations through a community addition one day?
							</p>
						</Column>
					</Row>
				</div>

			</Column>
		</Row>
	</div>
</body>

@code {
	private int seeValue = 86;
	bool seen = false;
	private int didValue = 14;
	bool did = false;

	void seenIt()
	{
		seen = !seen;
		if (seen) seeValue = 87;
		else seeValue = 86;
	}

	void didIt()
	{
		did = !did;
		if (did) didValue = 20;
		else seeValue = 14;
	}

	string at()
	{
		return "@";
	}
}
